'''苦菜'''（[[学名|学名]]：{{lang|la|''Sonchus oleraceus''}}），又名苦苣菜、滇苦荬菜、苦滇菜，为[[菊科|菊科]][[苦苣菜属|苦苣菜属]]的植物。原產於歐洲和西亞，後來擴散到全球，生长于海拔170米至3,200米的地区，多生长在林下、山坡、平地田间、空旷处、山谷林缘或近水处{{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070428180750/http://plants.ifas.ufl.edu/sonole.html |date=2007-04-28 }} at [http://plants.ifas.ufl.edu/welcome.html Center for Aquatic and Invasive Plants] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070325214633/http://plants.ifas.ufl.edu/welcome.html |date=2007-03-25 }}</ref><ref name="pier">[http://www.hear.org/pier/species/sonchus_oleraceus.htm Sonchus oleraceus L., Asteraceae] {{Wayback|url=http://www.hear.org/pier/species/sonchus_oleraceus.htm |date=20200202001414 }}, Pacific Island Ecosystems at Risk (PIER)</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Common sowthistle  ''Sonchus oleraceus''|url=http://www.weeds.org.au/cgi-bin/weedident.cgi?tpl=plant.tpl&state=&s=&ibra=all&card=H73|website=Weeds Australia|accessdate=25 September 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150328230835/http://www.weeds.org.au/cgi-bin/weedident.cgi?tpl=plant.tpl&state=&s=&ibra=all&card=H73|archive-date=2015-03-28|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

==特征==
[[File:2006-11-16Sonchus_oleraceus03-02.jpg|thumb]]
其莖中空，高度可達30-100釐米<ref>{{ cite book | first1=Yoshitaka | last1=Tanaka | first2=Nguyen | last2=Van Ke | date=2007 | title=Edible Wild Plants of Vietnam: The Bountiful Garden | publisher=Thailand: Orchid Press | isbn=9745240893 | page=52}}</ref>。性喜陽，對土壤要求不高。

